<rss xmlns:ns0="http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom" version="2.0"><channel><title>罗翔说刑法 的 bilibili 空间</title><link>https://space.bilibili.com/517327498</link><ns0:link href="http://rss.ovh/bilibili/user/video/517327498" rel="self" type="application/rss+xml" /><description>罗翔说刑法 的 bilibili 空间 - Powered by RSSHub</description><generator>RSSHub</generator><webMaster>contact@rsshub.app (RSSHub)</webMaster><language>en</language><image><url>https://i1.hdslb.com/bfs/face/4e5d0a51273fe3f8fabc700b6a71bb8a38c9e21e.jpg</url><title>罗翔说刑法 的 bilibili 空间</title><link>https://space.bilibili.com/517327498</link></image><lastBuildDate>Sat, 06 Dec 2025 14:31:57 GMT</lastBuildDate><ttl>5</ttl><item><title>【罗翔】精神病人真的“杀人不犯法”吗？</title><description>&lt;iframe width="640" height="360" src="https://www.bilibili.com/blackboard/html5mobileplayer.html?aid=115579969085266&amp;amp;cid=&amp;amp;bvid=BV1b4ycBfEE8" frameborder="0" allowfullscreen="" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"&gt;&lt;/iframe&gt; &lt;br&gt; &lt;img src="https://i1.hdslb.com/bfs/archive/a9474ce8f825eab73100a18432859f8b745bcdb6.jpg" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"&gt;&lt;br&gt; 我们经常听说，精神病人杀人不负刑事责任。但是，这显然是对法律的误读。法律中说的是精神病人在不能辨认或不能控制自己行为的时候，经法定程序确认的才不负刑事责任。而没有说精神病人一律不负刑事责任。</description><link>https://www.bilibili.com/video/BV1b4ycBfEE8</link><guid isPermaLink="false">https://www.bilibili.com/video/BV1b4ycBfEE8</guid><pubDate>Thu, 20 Nov 2025 03:48:23 GMT</pubDate><author>罗翔说刑法</author></item><item><title>【罗翔】看到路人被车撞打电话报警就要负责到底吗？</title><description>&lt;iframe width="640" height="360" src="https://www.bilibili.com/blackboard/html5mobileplayer.html?aid=115561967129116&amp;amp;cid=&amp;amp;bvid=BV1uLCaByEJ2" frameborder="0" allowfullscreen="" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"&gt;&lt;/iframe&gt; &lt;br&gt; &lt;img src="https://i1.hdslb.com/bfs/archive/579acdb75f5b03b2673bf1f07162219334f30a93.jpg" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"&gt;&lt;br&gt; 这几天有很多朋友发给我一个“触发救助义务”的视频，说是“不救人就没事，救人反而要负责到底”，这是真的吗？</description><link>https://www.bilibili.com/video/BV1uLCaByEJ2</link><guid isPermaLink="false">https://www.bilibili.com/video/BV1uLCaByEJ2</guid><pubDate>Mon, 17 Nov 2025 04:00:25 GMT</pubDate><author>罗翔说刑法</author></item><item><title>【罗翔】张三想“我以为她死了？这是故意杀人吗？”</title><description>&lt;iframe width="640" height="360" src="https://www.bilibili.com/blackboard/html5mobileplayer.html?aid=115545525456964&amp;amp;cid=&amp;amp;bvid=BV1m5CTBMEjT" frameborder="0" allowfullscreen="" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"&gt;&lt;/iframe&gt; &lt;br&gt; &lt;img src="https://i0.hdslb.com/bfs/archive/0bea76a94cb057a921721ff68f21fbfcf3733754.jpg" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"&gt;&lt;br&gt; 张三实施故意杀人，以为妻子已经死亡，所以将妻子从山崖抛下，想要制造妻子自杀的假象，但事实上妻子死于高空坠落。这应该如何定性呢？</description><link>https://www.bilibili.com/video/BV1m5CTBMEjT</link><guid isPermaLink="false">https://www.bilibili.com/video/BV1m5CTBMEjT</guid><pubDate>Fri, 14 Nov 2025 04:00:26 GMT</pubDate><author>罗翔说刑法</author></item><item><title>【罗翔】张三损毁电梯犯什么罪？电梯属于电车吗？是公共交通工具吗？</title><description>&lt;iframe width="640" height="360" src="https://www.bilibili.com/blackboard/html5mobileplayer.html?aid=115489657397031&amp;amp;cid=&amp;amp;bvid=BV1Vr1kBsEUv" frameborder="0" allowfullscreen="" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"&gt;&lt;/iframe&gt; &lt;br&gt; &lt;img src="https://i0.hdslb.com/bfs/archive/bf1eea3f7ccd974ce799ad36885071e16d808709.jpg" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"&gt;&lt;br&gt; 损毁电梯危及公共安全犯什么罪？</description><link>https://www.bilibili.com/video/BV1Vr1kBsEUv</link><guid isPermaLink="false">https://www.bilibili.com/video/BV1Vr1kBsEUv</guid><pubDate>Tue, 04 Nov 2025 05:03:04 GMT</pubDate><author>罗翔说刑法</author></item><item><title>【罗翔】死缓还不够，犯人上诉要求给自己加刑？</title><description>&lt;iframe width="640" height="360" src="https://www.bilibili.com/blackboard/html5mobileplayer.html?aid=115450734188614&amp;amp;cid=&amp;amp;bvid=BV1UdyBBeEaJ" frameborder="0" allowfullscreen="" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"&gt;&lt;/iframe&gt; &lt;br&gt; &lt;img src="https://i2.hdslb.com/bfs/archive/afffcffcbc1f4c2f456a33cf9f31f506ea1fb52e.jpg" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"&gt;&lt;br&gt; 这是一个真实的案例，今天我们讲讲上诉不加刑制度。</description><link>https://www.bilibili.com/video/BV1UdyBBeEaJ</link><guid isPermaLink="false">https://www.bilibili.com/video/BV1UdyBBeEaJ</guid><pubDate>Tue, 28 Oct 2025 10:05:02 GMT</pubDate><author>罗翔说刑法</author></item><item><title>【罗翔】一碗肥肠炒面救了两个人的命？什么是犯罪预备？</title><description>&lt;iframe width="640" height="360" src="https://www.bilibili.com/blackboard/html5mobileplayer.html?aid=115433588004816&amp;amp;cid=&amp;amp;bvid=BV1JgsRzaEGL" frameborder="0" allowfullscreen="" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"&gt;&lt;/iframe&gt; &lt;br&gt; &lt;img src="https://i1.hdslb.com/bfs/archive/c354d17579ec415f133e51307a29afdfd65db310.jpg" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"&gt;&lt;br&gt; 张三因情感纠纷，尾随妻子的情人，并购买水果刀企图杀害对方，结果走着走着就饿了，就去吃了碗肥肠炒面，这碗面阻止了张三实施更大错误。</description><link>https://www.bilibili.com/video/BV1JgsRzaEGL</link><guid isPermaLink="false">https://www.bilibili.com/video/BV1JgsRzaEGL</guid><pubDate>Sat, 25 Oct 2025 09:25:01 GMT</pubDate><author>罗翔说刑法</author></item><item><title>【罗翔】在家加班生病了，这算工伤吗？</title><description>&lt;iframe width="640" height="360" src="https://www.bilibili.com/blackboard/html5mobileplayer.html?aid=115380974590775&amp;amp;cid=&amp;amp;bvid=BV1UcWazLEyg" frameborder="0" allowfullscreen="" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"&gt;&lt;/iframe&gt; &lt;br&gt; &lt;img src="https://i1.hdslb.com/bfs/archive/c4fb6f1c231ebba77281715dca37d8b69815804a.jpg" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"&gt;&lt;br&gt; 针对这个问题我专门学习了一下劳动法，这期视频咱们聊一下这个问题。</description><link>https://www.bilibili.com/video/BV1UcWazLEyg</link><guid isPermaLink="false">https://www.bilibili.com/video/BV1UcWazLEyg</guid><pubDate>Thu, 16 Oct 2025 03:30:04 GMT</pubDate><author>罗翔说刑法</author></item><item><title>【罗翔】进入合租者房间偷拍隐私视频，该当何罪？</title><description>&lt;iframe width="640" height="360" src="https://www.bilibili.com/blackboard/html5mobileplayer.html?aid=115347973741872&amp;amp;cid=&amp;amp;bvid=BV1Va4EztEak" frameborder="0" allowfullscreen="" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"&gt;&lt;/iframe&gt; &lt;br&gt; &lt;img src="https://i2.hdslb.com/bfs/archive/44e87c7964e3977651fc530267feb408fb126482.jpg" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"&gt;&lt;br&gt; 张三和一位女生合租，居然在女生房间偷偷安装了一个小型摄像头，而且还多次进入房间调试拍摄视角，通过手机App偷窥女生的隐私。这种行为属于什么犯罪？</description><link>https://www.bilibili.com/video/BV1Va4EztEak</link><guid isPermaLink="false">https://www.bilibili.com/video/BV1Va4EztEak</guid><pubDate>Fri, 10 Oct 2025 04:32:04 GMT</pubDate><author>罗翔说刑法</author></item><item><title>【罗翔】炸裂的英国摩根案，性侵犯罪中的法律认识错误</title><description>&lt;iframe width="640" height="360" src="https://www.bilibili.com/blackboard/html5mobileplayer.html?aid=115264003772994&amp;amp;cid=&amp;amp;bvid=BV1Rin4zNEyU" frameborder="0" allowfullscreen="" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"&gt;&lt;/iframe&gt; &lt;br&gt; &lt;img src="https://i2.hdslb.com/bfs/archive/afb68b6b209c567bf5444c46dee54e5b15b260ad.jpg" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"&gt;&lt;br&gt; 摩根是一位皇家海军官员，一晚他与三位同事一起喝酒，酒后摩根邀请三位朋友和自己妻子发生性行为。他告诉三位朋友，如果他的妻子反抗，那是假装的，她的真实想法其实是同意，而且暴力会让她更加兴奋。于是这三位男性不顾摩根妻子的反抗和她发生了性行为。最后这三位男性被控强奸，但他们认为自己当时确实认为女方同意了。这个案件最终是如何判决的？</description><link>https://www.bilibili.com/video/BV1Rin4zNEyU</link><guid isPermaLink="false">https://www.bilibili.com/video/BV1Rin4zNEyU</guid><pubDate>Thu, 25 Sep 2025 08:33:50 GMT</pubDate><author>罗翔说刑法</author></item><item><title>【罗翔】性侵犯还能是过失犯罪？性侵犯罪中的事实认识错误</title><description>&lt;iframe width="640" height="360" src="https://www.bilibili.com/blackboard/html5mobileplayer.html?aid=115228603980839&amp;amp;cid=&amp;amp;bvid=BV1ZCWgzTEdr" frameborder="0" allowfullscreen="" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"&gt;&lt;/iframe&gt; &lt;br&gt; &lt;img src="https://i1.hdslb.com/bfs/archive/2f58e90efa2f6f349738b296ea4a87da41f63bf2.jpg" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"&gt;&lt;br&gt; 性侵犯罪是一种故意犯罪，有同学说，这多新鲜啊，性侵犯罪肯定是故意啊。但其实你去看法条，无论是刑法第236条强奸罪、236条之一的负有照护职责人员性侵罪、237条的强制猥亵、侮辱罪和猥亵儿童罪，所以你凭啥说性侵犯罪就一定是故意犯罪呢？我们今天就来聊聊性侵犯罪中的事实认识错误。</description><link>https://www.bilibili.com/video/BV1ZCWgzTEdr</link><guid isPermaLink="false">https://www.bilibili.com/video/BV1ZCWgzTEdr</guid><pubDate>Fri, 19 Sep 2025 04:30:02 GMT</pubDate><author>罗翔说刑法</author></item></channel></rss>